General.Name: G1 Secure Solutions Ltd
General.Description: G1 Secure Solutions Ltd provides security and safety services in Israel. The company operates through Technologies, Security, Monitoring, and Hotel divisions. It offers security solutions for home and businesses, fire detection and extinguishing, control center and patrol, cleaning, loss prevention, physical security, human resources, communication infrastructure, multimedia, mirroring systems, and smart security solutions. The company was incorporated in 1937 and is based in Petah Tikva, Israel.
